          <p style="color:#fff;font-weight:800;font-size:0.95rem;margin:0 0 6px;">Dubai Office</p>
          <p style="color:#94A3B8;font-size:0.95rem;line-height:1.7;margin:0;">Mob: [Add Mobile Number]<br/>Tel: [Add Landline Number]</p>
        </div>
        <p style="color:#94A3B8;font-size:0.9rem;margin:0;">[Add Email Address]</p>
